Now there is no one to comfort
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
Of all those that loved her.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
All her friends have proved faithless,
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
And turned to be foes.
\par}

