\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 10}The foeman hath stretched out his hand
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
To secure all her treasures.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
The hearthen she saw enter in
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
And her temple profane\uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
Even those Thou forbadest to mix
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
With Thine own congregation.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
 {\super\cf2\fs24 11}Her people all groan and moan
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
In their search after bread.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
They have given away their treasures
\par}

{\pard\fi-2080\li2800
For food to revive them.
\par}

{\pard\fi-2440\li2800
